Introduction

Jo Kyungmin is a South Korean singer under MNH Entertainment. He made his official debut as a member of the boy group 8TURN on January 30th, 2023.

Kyungmin was first known for being a participant in the survival show "I-LAND" and a former pre-debut member of &TEAM.
